<refsect1 id="VS-X-1a">
<title>Example</title>
<para>This example renders XML with XSLT, and demonstrates the following:</para>
<itemizedlist mark="bullet">
  <listitem>Shows the style sheet in a database table as well as in the file system.</listitem>
  <listitem>Shows use of the http_xslt() function to process XML with an XSL.</listitem>
  <listitem>Resolving the stylesheet reference, e.g. virt://, DAV resident sheets.</listitem>
  <listitem>Changing the stylesheet and when the sheet changes it is automatically detected.</listitem>
  <listitem>Affecting the output character set.</listitem>
  <listitem>Specifying parameters to the output xslt run.</listitem>
</itemizedlist>
</refsect1>
